此地點並沒有公共小巴或巴士直達或到達；唯源·區設有穿梭巴士來往屯門[[V_city|V city]]及源·區，並需要預約<ref>{{Cite web|title=【親子好去處】屯門 T · PARK [源 · 區] 全攻略 {{!}} Blog|url=https://www.sundaykiss.com/186617/blog_sundaykiss/【親子好去處】屯門-t-·-park-源-·-區-全攻略/|accessdate=2019-07-20|author=Sundaykiss|date=2016-10-12|format=|work=|publisher=|language=zh-hk|archive-date=2020-10-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201031191214/https://www.sundaykiss.com/186617/blog_sundaykiss/%E3%80%90%E8%A6%AA%E5%AD%90%E5%A5%BD%E5%8E%BB%E8%99%95%E3%80%91%E5%B1%AF%E9%96%80-t-%C2%B7-park-%E6%BA%90-%C2%B7-%E5%8D%80-%E5%85%A8%E6%94%BB%E7%95%A5/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。一般市民可以自行由[[屯門曾咀靈灰安置所|屯門曾咀靈灰安置所]]下車後，經[[稔灣路|稔灣路]]前往<ref>{{cite news |author1=香港經濟日報 HKET |title=屯門焚化爐轉廢為能 冷暖水療免費任玩 |url=https://topick.hket.com/article/1429159/屯門焚化爐轉廢為能%20冷暖水療免費任玩 |accessdate=2019-07-18 |date=2016-05-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161128100735/http://topick.hket.com/article/1429159/%E5%B1%AF%E9%96%80%E7%84%9A%E5%8C%96%E7%88%90%E8%BD%89%E5%BB%A2%E7%82%BA%E8%83%BD%20%E5%86%B7%E6%9A%96%E6%B0%B4%E7%99%82%E5%85%8D%E8%B2%BB%E4%BB%BB%E7%8E%A9 |archive-date=2016-11-28 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

